msgid ""
"This target emulates the behavior of bad sectors at arbitrary locations, and "
"the ability to enable the emulation of the failures at an arbitrary time."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/device-mapper/dm-dust.rst:8
msgid ""
"This target behaves similarly to a linear target.  At a given time, the user "
"can send a message to the target to start failing read requests on specific "
"blocks (to emulate the behavior of a hard disk drive with bad sectors)."
msgstr ""

